main home - Browse job listings with advanced filters (location, salary, type, skills).
header / job card - Save favorite jobs for later reference.
job detail / job seekers follow page - Apply for jobs and manage applications and show notifications.
job seekers profile -  Build and update profiles and resumes.

Employers follow page - Post job openings and manage job listings.
Employers applications page - View, filter, and manage applicants.
Employers applications page upplayer communication - Interact with candidates via real-time notifications.

Admin dashboard - Manage users, job listings, and reports effectively.

